   November 7, 2001



           JGR special section on Solar Eruptive Events Published

   Journal of Geophysical Research - Space Physics - has just published
   the special section on solar eruptive events (Vol. 106, No. A11,
   November 1, 2001). The issue also contains several related papers.

   The whole issue can be purchased directly from AGU for $20.
