   April 27, 2001

     JGR Special Section on Global picture of Solar Eruptive Events
   A special section in JGR space Physics is getting ready to be published
   sometime this summer. About 20 papers on solar eruptive events based on
   the international conference and the 1999 ISTP/IACG workshop will
   appear in the special section. One can purchase a single issue of
   JGR-Space Physics containing the special section for $20 (non members
   of AGU: $40). To get an idea of the contents of the special section,
   Please see the introduction to the special section. You may contact the
   AGU directly to purchase the issue.
